{"tid":1336951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朝早做樂師！夜晚做消防！水桶加麵包棍！","createTime":"2019-07-21T07:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T07:01:45.000Z","uid":258191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dd61afb261a2fd5592db2ba25d3dceccdf5568b3","tid":1336951,"uid":258191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T07:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sqmAJGo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsqmAJGo.png&h=42d46f20&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b4zFUN3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb4zFUN3.png&h=30ff0bc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n細細個見到啲人打鼓好羨慕但係無錢學，但係發現音樂呢啲嘢在心中！有心就可以係樂師！<br />\n<br />\n不過細細個又有另一個夢想係做<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">消防員</span></span>，諗起夜晚可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">張啲火頭撲熄</span></span>係兒時心願<br />\n<br />\n如果可以日頭玩音樂夜晚救人係我夢想！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見好似冇乜人買物資會買水桶，最後呼籲一下同路人買水桶做消防！！！多一個就多一個啦！！！"},{"pid":"ec98853eff53dd76dfd052840d8f2ec05d3adad6","tid":1336951,"uid":258191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T07:00:26.000Z","msg":"臨出門一推"},{"pid":"de5a87e2f86422ffa24b5bb27a08099faa3624aa","tid":1336951,"uid":258191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T07:01:00.000Z","msg":"中和龍蛋！中排有責！"},{"pid":"d2036dba3140e4bcfb0dc7dd18df518d569be5e3","tid":1336951,"uid":258191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T07:01:45.000Z","msg":"推"}]}